high_descs: Turn around and go to the white table behind you.
Close and pick up the laptop on the right corner closest to you.
Turn to your right and walk across the room, past the TV, to the white end table on your right.
Put the laptop to the right of the female statue, on the white end table.
anns.task_desc: Put a laptop on the end table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the white table with chairs.
Close the laptop on the table and pick it up.
Walk towards the yellow chair, turn right and face the white dresser with a statue.
Put the laptop on the table next to the statue.
anns.task_desc: Move the laptop from the table to the dresser with a statue.

high_descs: Turn left and take a small step then turn left and walk to the table.
Close the laptop and then pick it up off of the table.
Turn right and walk to the tv stand then take a small step to your left to clear the tv stand then walk to the chair in front of you and turn right when you get there.
Put the laptop to the right of the statue on the small white table.
